        <content type="html" xml:base="https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/blog/nighthaunt/">&lt;p&gt;Recently I&#x27;ve been a little obsessed with the Warcry tabletop skirmish game by Games workshop. I picked it up during lock-down and fell it love with it&#x27;s fast &amp;amp; flowing pace and it&#x27;s simple rules. For my Nighthaunt warband I wanted a quick to paint yet striking theme so decided to go for an etherial bluey-green colour for the ghosts and high contrast purple bases. I think it gives the warband striking retro-futuristic &#x2F; vaporwave vibes!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




